timing_enable...t_nets_support(25.10)    timing_enable...t_nets_support(25.10)

Name
       timing_enable_hierarchical_get_nets_support

Syntax
       timing_enable_hierarchical_get_nets_support {true | false}

       Default: false

       Enables hierarchical segment support for the get_nets command.

       When set to false, the get_nets command will report only flat nets.

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

